rubric.en:
Expected code/algorithm:
eqTest(a, b) {
  n = a.size();
  i = uniformNat(n);
  for (j = 0; j < n-1; ++j)
    if (a[i] == b[j]) return <i,j>;
  return <i, n-1>;
}

